  "title": "Retail Sales Associate (Automotive)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Greet customers and assist with selecting car care products and accessories.</li>\n  <li>Provide basic advice on lubricants, car maintenance items, and accessories.</li>\n  <li>Educate customers on product benefits, usage, and simple maintenance tips.</li>\n  <li>Assist and guide customers on using digital payments and loyalty features.</li>\n  <li>Recommend fuels, promotions, and car care services.</li>\n  <li>Handle customer inquiries on car care, car wash, and servicing options.</li>\n  <li>Assist customers with booking car servicing appointments.</li>\n  <li>Work closely with station staff, retailers, and operators.</li>\n  <li>Perform windscreen cleaning, wiper checks, and wiper replacements.</li>\n  <li>Conduct basic checks for ICE, Hybrid, and EV vehicles (fluids, battery health, tyre tread).</li>\n  <li>Help monitor inventory and alert supervisors when stock is low.</li>\n  <li>Perform any other duties assigned by the supervisor.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>ITE Certificate / Diploma</li>\n  <li>Nitec / Higher Nitec in Automotive, Mechanical, or Service-related fields</li>\n  <li>Basic understanding of car cleaning and maintenance.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>EA License No: 19C9611</p>\n<p>EA Personnel Reg No: R1433735 Teng Wei Mun (Celest)</p>",
